      "category": "language",
      "body": "The phrase \"heavy sleep\" is associated with deep sleep. The adjective ‘heavy' can also stand for \"slow, sluggish, dull\" (Schmidt 5) and \"weary, drowsy, sleepy\" (Schmidt 6). ",
